281
00:21:15,340 --> 00:21:17,069
Angry enough to do something about it?

282
00:21:17,142 --> 00:21:18,473
Take revenge in some kind of way?

283
00:21:18,543 --> 00:21:19,771
You think I have something
to do with this guy?

284
00:21:19,845 --> 00:21:22,245
- Do you?
- I'm telling you the truth. I...

285
00:21:22,648 --> 00:21:24,013
I heard his voice.

286
00:21:27,452 --> 00:21:28,942
Do you have some place you gotta be?

287
00:21:29,021 --> 00:21:30,818
It's my wife, yes. I have a meeting...

288
00:21:30,889 --> 00:21:31,913
At a what?

289
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:33,514
At a therapy session.

290
00:21:34,493 --> 00:21:36,825
It's couples counseling. We're...

291
00:21:38,730 --> 00:21:40,891
