292
00:21:44,136 --> 00:21:45,660
<i>This guy's worthless.</i>

293
00:21:46,938 --> 00:21:48,870
Yeah, I was real sorry
to hear about your father.

294
00:21:49,074 --> 00:21:51,372
He seemed like a good guy.

295
00:21:53,378 --> 00:21:55,869
Man, I thought I was a slob.

296
00:21:57,082 --> 00:21:58,572
They were here, too.

297
00:21:58,717 --> 00:22:00,378
- What?
- Nothing.

298
00:22:00,452 --> 00:22:02,249
I got a guy who can clean this
up for 100 bucks.

299
00:22:02,321 --> 00:22:04,585
No. It's all right. I'll take it as it is.

300
00:22:04,656 --> 00:22:06,146
We rent by the week.

301
00:22:06,858 --> 00:22:08,587
I'm gonna need to know you can afford it.

302
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:09,854
I have a job.

303
00:22:09,928 --> 00:22:11,054
Doing what?

304
