324
00:25:07,772 --> 00:25:09,399
That's on top of the tuition.

325
00:25:09,474 --> 00:25:13,433
About the tuition. Your last
three checks have bounced.

326
00:25:13,512 --> 00:25:15,343
Fine, take it out of the 25 grand
that I gave you.

327
00:25:15,413 --> 00:25:18,576
That was a donation. And it was
