455
00:33:43,955 --> 00:33:45,547
One, two, three...

456
00:33:48,659 --> 00:33:50,593

457
00:33:58,736 --> 00:34:00,636
I missed you, Amid.

458
00:34:01,305 --> 00:34:04,069
Our bond is too strong
to be broken by a woman.

459
00:34:06,477 --> 00:34:08,707
We are bound by our beliefs.

460
00:34:09,313 --> 00:34:11,543
I don't believe in anything anymore.

461
00:34:12,450 --> 00:34:14,782
We trained together, we prayed together,

462
00:34:14,852 --> 00:34:17,412
went on haj together, we're still brothers.

463
00:34:17,722 --> 00:34:18,950
You flatter yourself.

464
00:34:19,023 --> 00:34:21,992
