472
00:34:45,516 --> 00:34:49,213
We started this together,
we need to finish it together.

473
00:34:50,388 --> 00:34:53,323
Allah forgives you, so do I.

474
00:34:56,160 --> 00:34:58,492
We can't do this without you.

475
00:35:02,867 --> 00:35:05,165
It's because of her, isn't it?

476
00:35:09,474 --> 00:35:12,739
I killed someone I loved.
I killed my own wife.

477
00:35:15,413 --> 00:35:17,745
I will not kill anyone else.

478
00:35:19,650 --> 00:35:22,619
What are you talking about?
She died of cancer.

479
00:35:23,488 --> 00:35:24,978
I read the obituary.

480
00:35:25,857 --> 00:35:27,415
When they bombed our camp in Pakistan,

481
00:35:27,492 --> 00:35:30,484
